    "description": "Unboxing offers a meditative and relaxing experience. Satisfy your mind while unboxing, scraping, and selling intrinsic items.<br>Use drones to automate your job and watch them work for you.<br>Upgrade to new contracts and increase your chance to unbox more items.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2179770/extras/d5892869f3d25d524ce54e7b23300268.poster.avif?t=1685477953\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2179770/extras/d5892869f3d25d524ce54e7b23300268.webm?t=1685477953\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2179770/extras/d5892869f3d25d524ce54e7b23300268.mp4?t=1685477953\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Before you buy</strong><br>I created Unboxing to reach a personal goal: Develop the best game I could, with good quality, visuals, and audio, in a determined period.<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>No, I didn't model all the objects myself.<br></li><li>No, we don't have triple-A features.<br></li><li>No, we don't have Hollywood soundtracks.</li></ul><br><strong>What you should expect</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Satisfying and Relaxing Soundtrack<br></li><li>Futuristic Environment<br></li><li>12 Different Crates to Unbox<br></li><li>47 Different Items to Loot<br></li><li>Cool Diegetic UI</li></ul><br><strong>What you should not expect</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Massive Multiplayer Online<br></li><li>Violence and Gore<br></li><li>Pay to Win Store<br></li><li>Advertisements</li></ul>",
